title: Microangelo Toolset 6.10.8.zip

Microangelo Toolset 6.10.8.0 - 2008





Toolset includes an icon editor that creates and edits icons. Its four integrated components work together to create, edit, access, find, extract, filter, and manipulate icons and the images they contain. Toolset provides a solid foundation of icon tools used by today's (and tomorrow's) icon masters.

*Create and edit icons in all sizes and formats withToolset's icon editor.

*Make icons from PSD, PNG, JPG, or BMP files.

*Edit icons inside ICO, ICL, EXE, DLL, and other program files.

*Change program icons using a Windows interface or the command line.

*Search and extract icons from icon resources, libraries and program files.

*Make animated cursors with Animator, Toolset's animated cursor editor
